The Artist Next Level Podcast with Sergio Gomez

With over 300 episodes and thousands of monthly downloads from artists around the world, the Art NXT Level weekly podcast provides artists and art lovers alike with behind the scenes stories from artists, curators, gallery owners and other professionals in and outside of the art world. The focus of the podcast is to provide ideas, tools, resources and inspiration for the contemporary artist. The podcast is available for download at iTunes, Google Play, iHeart Radio, Spotify and many others.

Previous guest include Rebecca Wilson (Curator, Saatchi Art), Tony Karman (Director, ExpoChicago), Nicole Berry (Deputy, The Armory Show), Tim Okamura (artist), Dan Addington (Owner, Addington Gallery), Edra Soto (artist), Steven and Elaine Bennett (The Bennett Prize) among many others.

Subscribe in iTunes and give us a review.
